  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.64,
    "endTime": 186.736,
    "text": "and that music spread all over the world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.76,
    "endTime": 189.136,
    "text": "And the songs that I'm singing tonight"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.16,
    "endTime": 192.656,
    "text": "are from an album that I just put out called, \"Playing Chess,\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.68,
